      <lg xml:id="TVM2.4.11">
<l>vāṭṭa miṟpukaḻ vāmaṉaṉaiyicai</l>
<l>kūṭṭi vaṇcaṭa kōpaṉcollamai</l>
<l>pāṭṭō rāyirat tippattālaṭi</l>
<l>cūṭṭa lākuman tāmamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Adorning [his] feet</l>
<l>with these ten among the one thousand of songs</l>
<l>fashioned in words, joining music, by generous</l>
<l>Caṭakōpaṉ on the Dwarf of unfading fame</l>
	<l>is highest heaven.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
